Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋老師跟木村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現代國語的木村和現代保健的守屋老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有勇氣呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣...嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到現時為止有沒有不明白的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟木村老師交往的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雄蕊已經
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓雌蕊受了精嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送子鳥已經來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在高麗菜田裡撿到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候會生孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 果然會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是無法地帶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 木村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是怎麼跟守屋老師開始交往的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼... 我們的故鄉是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後聊一聊發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還蠻投機...的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是同鄉的羈絆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯... 咦? 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一起吃午餐嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好閃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人嚮往當個新娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,式的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才...才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的個性不合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得妳的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是當新娘子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候的事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在背乘法的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一位很像新娘的人出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 是...是誰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像不能說話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為太年幼了 所以意識很薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生前的記憶好像沒什麼留著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話可能會發生不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有心願沒有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會化作鬼魂留在這個世上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個少女的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻在漸漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能會在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能了結心願的情況下消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼會!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗屋?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 來製造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名為回憶的新牽絆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就好了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說得很好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是 覺得..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很令人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來教她說話吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以溝通比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這樣她就會叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也說不定呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是傻瓜山田喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗屋?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜山田!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學得真快~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後這傢伙是紅髮的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人可以揍 真的很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上原同學~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人叫井上成美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對比自己年長的人要加稱謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用背影害羞!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全混熟了的感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她說了些什麼啊? 老髮髻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是少數派 所以忍不住...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是也~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天來學習怎麼跟人打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成美~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 井上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要在看我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜...拜...拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道別時用的話喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔~ 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的份我也買了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候要說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歹勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說歹勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反被教育!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要多注意一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YEH~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩接龍合戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(MO)開始的字是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 斗屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜥蝪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗髮柔順劑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 水蜜桃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗屋!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙太寵她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 在一起 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都好高大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身高嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得挺會說話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是什麼也想不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這句話到底是什麼意思 也還是個謎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是想不起來也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還有我們這班知心的好友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說得很好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是總覺得有點火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 是老師他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也很閃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守...屋?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這孩子跟守屋老師是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實守屋被附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是守屋老師的私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其...實是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋老師的守護靈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有其他的想法嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 暫時沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆讓她跟守屋老師見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太讚成那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道那個少女是什麼人的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一讓守屋殿下受到什麼傷害的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個會有什害啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊... 我只是說萬一而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說...說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為守屋老師跟木村老師快要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 用些溫和一點的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就由我來調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋老師跟這個孩子的關係!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都查不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑著蠻混過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微不好意思一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我們去調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又...又不是為了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了守屋老師他們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傲驕 傲驕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要教她奇怪的話啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海就陪著這個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 很忙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們二人一起玩吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來好像有什麼煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被人發現的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 忍不住...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被老師發現的話就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菜快做好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...嗯 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的是幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你陪著她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為什麼? 有種令人懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄好了 吃多點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個女孩子的幽靈在找守屋老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直說"守屋守屋"這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道那孩子長得怎麼樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔... 頭髮長長的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著一件白色的連身裙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不是連身裙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是住院的時候會穿上的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 守屋老師他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候身體很虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常常進出醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也住院住過很長一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個孩子跟他同房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為年齡相近 所以很快就成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩耍喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個孩子的病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比他嚴重得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡飯真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋老師 今天真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣 別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的體驗也很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們要玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我明天妹辦法玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要舉行婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋...要結婚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋 很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經是大人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也已經會吃蘿蔔了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 那個孩子是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是守屋老師小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住院時認識的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是小孩子 代表...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不一起玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說我要陪他玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上同學...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔~喔~ 好逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不老實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩什麼好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好~! 來玩踢罐子吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你來當鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那個~拿回來~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始了嗎~?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔... 天海?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要來一起玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救世主就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是傻瓜山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我傻瓜啊~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的玩得很盡興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩得開心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果... 可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一直 留在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 剛剛的是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這睡相!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再睡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說拜拜了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海 大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我玩那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守屋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成大人...的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變帥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要再見面喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法守約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是! 我最喜歡守屋了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜~ 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們慢慢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走很多的遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿著很多的手信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 一起去見那個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊... 總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還要打工 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工什麼的 曠職吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是朋友對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看氣氛好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又沒關係...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡有人缺席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎? 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就 讓山田請客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等...為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,語言這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為知道它的意思才用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「再見」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用學起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子跟我說了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「謝謝你們陪我玩了那麼久」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再玩久一點也沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 天海同學你們也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也是 後天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一直一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告什麼的超麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是女高中的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼時代的情人節都一樣呢
